" change leader to space
map <space> <leader>

" normal mappings 
" ===============
nnoremap <leader>nh :nohlsearch<CR>
nnoremap <leader>nn :set nonumber<CR>
nnoremap <leader>nm :set number<CR>

" insert mappings
" ===============
inoremap hjk <esc>
inoremap <C-h> <Left>
inoremap <C-j> <Down>
inoremap <C-k> <Up>
inoremap <C-l> <Right>
